{"word":"ἀντί","slug":"ἀντί","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<entryFree id=\"n9778\" key=\"a)nti/\" type=\"main\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"entryFree\"> <orth extent=\"full\" lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"orth\">ἀντί</orth>, Prep. governing gen.:—orig. sense, <sense id=\"n9778.0\" n=\"A\" level=\"1\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"sense\"> <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">over against.</tr_> (Cf. Skt. <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">a/nti</tr_> 'opposite', 'facing', Lat. <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">ante,</tr_> etc.) </sense> <sense n=\"A\" id=\"n9778.1\" level=\"1\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"sense\"> USAGE: </sense> <sense n=\"I\" id=\"n9778.2\" level=\"2\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"sense\"> of Place, <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">opposite, over against,</tr_> formerly quoted from several places of <bibl default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\">Hom.</author></bibl>, as <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg001.perseus-grc1:21:481\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Il.\">Il.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">21.481</biblScope> </bibl> <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">ἀντὶ ἐμεῖο</foreign> (where now <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">ἀντί᾽ ἐμεῖο,</foreign> i.e. <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">ἀντία</foreign>)<foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">Τρώων ἄνθ᾽ ἑκατόν</foreign> (i.e. <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">ἄντα</foreign>) <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg001.perseus-grc1:8:233\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">8.233</biblScope> </bibl>; so <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">ἄντ᾽ Αἴαντος</foreign> (i.e. <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">ἄντα</foreign>) <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg001.perseus-grc1:15:415\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">15.415</biblScope></bibl>, cf. <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg002.perseus-grc1:4:115\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Od.\">Od.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">4.115</biblScope></bibl>, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0020.tlg002.perseus-grc1:727\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Hes.\">Hes.</a></author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Op.\">Op.</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">727</biblScope> </bibl>; but <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">ἀντί</foreign> is so used in <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0032.tlg006.perseus-grc1:4:7:6\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ X.\">X.</a></author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ An.\">An.</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">4.7.6</biblScope></bibl>, <bibl default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ IG\">IG</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">2.835</biblScope> </bibl> <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">c-l</tr_> <bibl default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">68</biblScope> </bibl>; <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">αἱ ὀπαὶ αἱ γιγνόμεναι ἀ. τόρμων</foreign> mortises <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">facing</tr_> tenons, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0559.tlg012:97:5\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Hero\">Hero</a></author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Bel.\">Bel.</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">97.5</biblScope> </bibl>; <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">ἀντὶ μαιτύρων</foreign> <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">in the presence of</tr_> witnesses, <bibl default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Leg.Gort.\">Leg.Gort.</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">1.40</biblScope> </bibl>; <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\